longBusinessSummary: Australian Goldfields Limited engages in the acquisition and exploration of mineral properties in Canada. The company was formerly known as Graphite Energy Corp. and changed its name to Australian Goldfields Limited in March 2021. Australian Goldfields Limited was incorporated in 2016 and is headquartered in Vancouver, Canada.
